DarkMouse::

She smiled. "Yeah, I can. Watch this."
She typed out the commands and watched as the screen showed the 
origins of the comms and where they were heading.  She smirked as she 
pressed a few more buttons and started hearing, with lots of static, 
what most of the comms were.  She could make out maximal 
transmissions as well as Pred. "Well, It's really fuzzy, but I think 
there's a new bot in town and everyone is trying to get the jump on 
it. What do you think?"
